 * {@link AllocationDecider} that implements priority-based shard allocation constraints.
 *
 * <p>
 * This decider allows Elasticsearch to preferentially allocate shards from high-priority
 * indices to high-performance (premium-tier) nodes, while gracefully degrading to
 * standard-tier nodes when necessary.
 * </p>
 *
